data.description: Open concept, hardwood floors on main level, carpet upstairs and on stairs. Eat-in Kitchen seats up to 5 around large island, wine cooler, stainless steal appliances, and a coffee bar area that seats 3. Powder room off the large living room. Laundry room and mud room from back of house. Grand stairway between living room and kitchen. Two bedrooms on main floor including a large master bedroom with walk-in closet and on bathroom. Two bedrooms up stairs with a full bathroom and an extra room for an office or kids game room. Off street parking or RV parking. Large back yard. Patio area in back and large front porch. Two car garage with storage loft area above. Unfinished basement with lots of storage space built in pantry and working ceramic kiln. Back yard is fully fenced with established garden boxes . Updated in ground sprinklers system Quite neighborhood next to Franklin school, park, museum and pool. Walking distant to schools, parks, shopping, and bus routes.
data.whatILove: Everything is up to date and all brand new stainless steal appliance, refrigerator has icemaker in bottom freezer. Open concept, built in wine cooler, bar area seating for 3, and large island with seating for 5. Large living room with grand staircase. Large master with walk-in closet, and own bathroom with double sinks. The two bedrooms upstairs have large walk-in closet, one bedroom with an egress sky light. The house is close to Franklin Park, there are three schools close by. Transportation, restraints, and stores in walking distance.
